---
import PortfolioLayout from '../layouts/PortfolioLayout.astro';
---

<PortfolioLayout
	title="Individual Work | ShangLi Zhou"
	description="DFS I individual work by ShangLi Zhou, with placeholder static and animated media."
>
	<section class="page-hero">
		<p class="eyebrow">Individual Work / 个人作品</p>
		<h1>DFS I</h1>
		<p>
			An individual project focused on gradually building a game engine and documenting the
			technical decisions behind the work.
		</p>
		<p class="cn">一个逐渐开始搭建游戏引擎的个人项目，用于记录技术实现、系统设计和开发过程。</p>
	</section>

	<section class="section">
		<div class="project-header">
			<div>
				<p class="section-label">Project</p>
				<h2>DFS I - Engine Foundation</h2>
			</div>
			<p class="tag">Individual Project</p>
		</div>
		<div class="copy-block wide">
			<p>
				DFS I is a placeholder portfolio entry for an individual engine-development project. The
				final version will show how I approach rendering, input, update loops, asset handling, and
				small gameplay tests as the engine grows from a technical base into a playable environment.
			</p>
			<p class="cn">
				DFS I 是一个个人引擎开发项目的占位展示。最终版本会展示我如何处理渲染、输入、更新循环、资源管理，
				以及如何通过小型玩法测试让引擎从技术基础逐渐变成可玩的环境。
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section media-grid">
		<article class="card media-card">
			<img src="/images/dfs-static-placeholder.svg" alt="DFS I static image placeholder" />
			<h3>Static Image</h3>
			<p>
				This placeholder will be replaced by a still screenshot of the DFS I engine or prototype
				state.
			</p>
			<p class="cn">此占位图将替换为 DFS I 引擎或原型状态的静态截图。</p>
		</article>
		<article class="card media-card">
			<img src="/images/dfs-animated-placeholder.svg" alt="DFS I animated image placeholder" />
			<h3>Animated Image</h3>
			<p>
				This placeholder will be replaced by a GIF or animated capture showing the project in
				motion.
			</p>
			<p class="cn">此占位图将替换为展示项目动态效果的 GIF 或动画录屏。</p>
		</article>
	</section>
</PortfolioLayout>
